rows.label: bf11210150_0010
rows.name:
It's good to see you again, Prince Adel.
Please forgive the actions of my guards.

rows.label: bf11210150_0020
rows.name: Don't you worry about it.

rows.label: bf11210150_0022
rows.name:
I'm just glad to see you well,
Your Imperial Majesty.

rows.label: bf11210150_0030
rows.name: Imperial...Majesty?

rows.label: bf11210150_0040
rows.name: May I introduce...

rows.label: bf11210150_0050
rows.name: Emperor of Superbia, Hugo el Superbia.

rows.label: bf11210150_0060
rows.name: The Superbian Emperor?!

rows.label: bf11210150_0070
rows.name: What's someone of his station doing out here?

rows.label: bf11210150_0080
rows.name: You know, our stations are fairly similar...

rows.label: bf11210150_0090
rows.name: Not that you'd ever know...

rows.label: bf11210150_0100
rows.name: Thanks! I try.

rows.label: bf11210150_0110
rows.name: I've come for the Holy Grail.

rows.label: bf11210150_0120
rows.name:
Its actions have been felt in Superbia,
as well. We're currently chasing it down.

rows.label: bf11210150_0130
rows.name: The same as us, then.

rows.label: bf11210150_0140
rows.name: But coming here yourself?

rows.label: bf11210150_0150
rows.name: My brother is ruling in my absence.

rows.label: bf11210150_0160
rows.name:
I see...
You brought Kagutsuchi and Wadatsumi?

rows.label: bf11210150_0170
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]?

rows.label: bf11210150_0180
rows.name:
Those two are the Crown Jewels
of the Superbian forces.

rows.label: bf11210150_0190
rows.name:
Wielding them on the front lines is the
duty of he who has the throne.

rows.label: bf11210150_0200
rows.name:
Indeed... That ought to have been my
older brother.

rows.label: bf11210150_0210
rows.name:
But he didn't have the potential to
become a Driver.

rows.label: bf11210150_0220
rows.name: And now, here you are,

rows.label: bf11210150_0222
rows.name: bonded with both of them.

rows.label: bf11210150_0230
rows.name:
The Special Inquisitor is under my
brother's direct command.

rows.label: bf11210150_0240
rows.name: Oh.

rows.label: bf11210150_0250
rows.name:
Should I fall in battle, he has his orders
to retrieve the Core Crystals.

rows.label: bf11210150_0260
rows.name: That sounds cold...

rows.label: bf11210150_0270
rows.name: That's how it goes with matters of state.

rows.label: bf11210150_0280
rows.name: And yet.

rows.label: bf11210150_0282
rows.name: It works out well for me.

rows.label: bf11210150_0290
rows.name:
I have always wanted to put myself
on the line for our people.

rows.label: bf11210150_0300
rows.name:
And I never enjoyed wielding authority
in the first place.

rows.label: bf11210150_0310
rows.name:
I feel the same way. I don't get why anyone
would want to sit on a throne.

rows.label: bf11210150_0320
rows.name:
Yes, that? If Prince Zettar knew,
there would be consequences.

rows.label: bf11210150_0330
rows.name: Let's...pretend you didn't hear me say that.

rows.label: bf11210150_0340
rows.name:
You two will never see eye to eye.
Better to leave well enough alone.

rows.label: bf11210150_0350
rows.name:
Ruling is...
Frankly, it's a scary thought.

rows.label: bf11210150_0360
rows.name:
Just imagine, becoming someone
you don't recognize...

rows.label: bf11210150_0370
rows.name:
Never knowing who's looking back
at you in the mirror...

rows.label: bf11210150_0380
rows.name: Prince Adel.

rows.label: bf11210150_0382
rows.name:
I'd be happy if you called me Hugo,
like old times.

rows.label: bf11210150_0390
rows.name:
I will, dear Hugo.
But only if you'll call me Adel in return.

rows.label: bf11210150_0400
rows.name:
Well, it would be beneficial to share our findings.
But perhaps elsewhere might be better?

rows.label: bf11210150_0410
rows.name: How about Your Majesty's flagship?

rows.label: bf11210150_0415
rows.name: Indeed.

rows.label: bf11210150_0420
rows.name: Flag...ship?

rows.label: bf11210150_0430
rows.name: Something the matter, Laura-sama?

rows.label: bf11210150_0440
rows.name:
I'm just...not very good in that kind of
stuffy environment...

rows.label: bf11210150_0450
rows.name: You're not alone there! That's the worst.

rows.label: bf11210150_0460
rows.name: Right?!

rows.label: bf11210150_0462
rows.name: I think I'll sit this particular venture out.

rows.label: bf11210150_0470
rows.name: Yeah, I'm out too.

rows.label: bf11210150_0480
rows.name: Oh no you don't.

rows.label: bf11210150_0490
rows.name: Wait a minute... Is that her?

rows.label: bf11210150_0500
rows.name: Yes. This is Hikari, one of the Holy Grails.

rows.label: bf11210150_0510
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: bf11210150_0520
rows.name: Your account would be valuable as well Laura.

rows.label: bf11210150_0530
rows.name:
Everything I've seen or heard,
Shin will know as well

rows.label: bf11210150_0540
rows.name: Ah, y-yes, that's true.

rows.label: bf11210150_0550
rows.name: Please, would you go instead of me please?

rows.label: bf11210150_0560
rows.name: Of course. I will do as you wish.

rows.label: bf11210150_0570
rows.name: Thank you kindly.

rows.label: bf11210150_0572
rows.name: Well then, shall we?
